{"tid":215840,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"友誼係咪真係咁脆弱？","createTime":"2017-04-24T16:28:21.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-24T23:36:42.000Z","uid":85644,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"619d89513dd70c5f08cae7014b16dbf35ceb07b8","tid":215840,"uid":85644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T16:28:21.000Z","msg":"我同佢本身成日都會互串<br />\n不過佢份人就比較情緒化 嬲嘅點好奇怪<br />\n我就從來冇對佢發脾氣 佢就間唔中都會發下<br />\n但係都算係好快無事 不過每一次係佢無理嘅發脾氣情況下 我都會諗依段友誼係咪應該結束呢？<br />\n因為某d原因我遲d應該唔可以同佢同一間學校<br />\n我一直都好珍惜同佢相處嘅時間<br />\n反而佢不斷令我覺得依段友誼有d辛苦 <br />\n加上今日又嘈過嚟 我係咪應該唔好再理佢？<br />\n等依段友誼慢慢淡？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申:我同佢都係絲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4276c265b1bf839b17ceb5dff64f519170151514","tid":215840,"uid":66657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T16:29:57.000Z","msg":"小小野就無frd做<br />\n咁叫友誼?<br />\n利申:巴 有個8年兄弟"},{"pid":"476cd9e5f42ddabb9cf515de25faccdac2c4c408","tid":215840,"uid":53794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T16:30:40.000Z","msg":"女人就係咁"},{"pid":"c017a5718967ca6d92aa617b1bee12f625a3b455","tid":215840,"uid":85644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T16:35:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>小小野就無frd做<br />\n咁叫友誼?<br />\n利申:巴 有個8年兄弟</blockquote><br />\n發生多幾次少少野 就唔同講法<br />\n我都忍左佢好多次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 講真其實我都唔想咁<br />\n巴打男仔冇女仔咁煩啊 佢啲脾氣有啲港女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95c0ae5ac267734aadaa19b8d3113a04d39fabce","tid":215840,"uid":8028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T16:46:27.000Z","msg":"友誼不嬲都脆弱 <br />\n<br />\n利申 曾經有三個以為係知己嘅人出現過 兩個反面一個比時間沖淡左"},{"pid":"b2403c3031a9458ad5cf49bab4b537521c902820","tid":215840,"uid":76514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T17:07:20.000Z","msg":"係女人之間既友情太脆弱...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a42b38a3b981485c65c2babfdcc74fa2eabca32","tid":215840,"uid":46894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T17:09:45.000Z","msg":"我都試過，最後頂唔順真係唔理佢"},{"pid":"79b7f552b4ed1b140c3fb9fa93e6844bcd566834","tid":215840,"uid":32973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T17:12:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係女人之間既友情太脆弱...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nagger<br />\n利申 巴 有個11年兄弟 幾個6年兄弟 大家互串又得乜都得 唔會反面"},{"pid":"fb2ce5eae1c17d42555eaa59d798b1780ae3cca9","tid":215840,"uid":99102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T19:07:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"01adf803c8502e425751dff750b329fb067dce5f","tid":215840,"uid":85644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T23:13:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>友誼不嬲都脆弱 <br />\n<br />\n利申 曾經有三個以為係知己嘅人出現過 兩個反面一個比時間沖淡左</blockquote><br />\n巴打我同你都差唔多 有兩個以前fd咗3年 分咗班之後就冇再聯絡過 一個去咗外國連wts都冇應<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5fde5963be011d3dceecf3e59640196f92e7b52f","tid":215840,"uid":85644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T23:16:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係,之前有個朋友因爲d好小既野而同我反左面，佢到而家都仲係好憎我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n但係今次嘈交嘅原因係因為有個男仔追佢 個男仔嘅樣同埋性格都係唔掂 我就講笑話受佢啦 我平時同其他fd都係會咁講笑 所以我覺得冇問題點知佢就嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁大家覺得依件係咪小事？"},{"pid":"672c4dd57eff220f197abf289f6e827cd3e425f0","tid":215840,"uid":65752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T23:36:42.000Z","msg":"女人有友誼既咩？"}]}